Contract_Value__c.calculatedFormula:
/* OLD FORMULA 
If( IsWon__c = true, (UnitPrice *  Quantity), 0)
*/

IF( IsWon__c, 
IF( 
AND( ISPICKVAL(Sales_Price_Type_Read_Only__c, "Annual Value"), Length_Days_Value__c > 31, ISPICKVAL(Service_Type__c, "Subscription")), 
UnitPrice*(Length_Days_Value__c/365),
UnitPrice
), 0)
Contract_Value__c.label: Contract Value
Contract_Value__c.name: Contract_Value__c

Renewal_Reason__c.label: Renewal Outcome

Annual_Value__c.calculatedFormula:
/* ORIGINAL FORMULA 
 IF(AND(Length_Days_Value__c > 31,  NOT(ISPICKVAL( Service_Type__c , "One-Time")) ) ,(UnitPrice/Length_Days_Value__c)*365,UnitPrice)
*/

IF( IsWon__c, 
IF( 
OR(ISPICKVAL(Sales_Price_Type_Read_Only__c, "Annual Value"), ISPICKVAL(Service_Type__c, "One-Time"), Length_Days_Value__c <= 31), 
UnitPrice , 
(UnitPrice/Length_Days_Value__c)*365
), 0)
Annual_Value__c.label: Annual Value
Annual_Value__c.name: Annual_Value__c

Cancellation_Amount__c.calculatedFormula: IF( AND(ISPICKVAL( Business_Type__c , "Renewal"),  (Annual_Value__c - Previous_Annual_Value__c) < 0  ) ,  ABS(Annual_Value__c - Previous_Annual_Value__c) , 0)
Cancellation_Amount__c.label: Cancellation Amount
Cancellation_Amount__c.name: Cancellation_Amount__c

Responsible_Party__c.calculatedFormula:
IF( 

CONTAINS( IF( ISBLANK( Salesperson__c ) ,  Opportunity.Owner_Role__c , Salesperson__r.UserRole.Name ), "ROW" ), 

IF( ISBLANK( Salesperson__c ) ,  Opportunity.Owner.FirstName + ' ' + Opportunity.Owner.LastName , Salesperson__r.FirstName + ' ' + Salesperson__r.LastName ),

IF( ISBLANK( Salesperson__c ) , Opportunity.Owner_Role__c , Salesperson__r.UserRole.Name )

)
Responsible_Party__c.label: Responsible Party
Responsible_Party__c.name: Responsible_Party__c

Sales_Team__c.calculatedFormula:
IF( ISBLANK( Salesperson__c ),  

IF(BEGINS(Opportunity.Owner_Role__c, "VP:"), 

RIGHT(Opportunity.Owner_Role__c, LEN(Opportunity.Owner_Role__c)-FIND(":", Opportunity.Owner_Role__c)-1), 

Opportunity.Owner_Role__c

)  

,  

IF(BEGINS(Salesperson__r.UserRole.Name, "VP:"), 

RIGHT(Salesperson__r.UserRole.Name, LEN(Salesperson__r.UserRole.Name)-FIND(":", Salesperson__r.UserRole.Name)-1), 

Salesperson__r.UserRole.Name

)   

)
Sales_Team__c.label: Sales Team
Sales_Team__c.name: Sales_Team__c

Salesperson_Name__c.calculatedFormula: IF( ISBLANK( Salesperson__c ),  Opportunity.Owner.FirstName + ' ' + Opportunity.Owner.LastName  , Salesperson__r.FirstName + ' ' + Salesperson__r.LastName )
